MY2023 : GG33. Date of Service for Laboratory Tests 
(Applies GG33) : Organizations may consider all events with dates no more than 7 days apart to be the same test and may use the collected date for reporting.

Pick all the dates in the Prior Year.
Pick the dates that have >4 result. (If the only >4 result is not in the PY, move to next step of prioritization.)
Pick primary over supplemental.
Pick latest date.
